EmailTemplate.description: Welcome Letter- Sent after EchoSign contract is signed and dealer was activated
EmailTemplate.name: OB: Welcome to SunPower - RES
EmailTemplate.subject: Welcome to SunPower
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Contact.FirstName}:
Thank you for making the choice to partner with SunPower. We are very excited to work with you through our North American Dealer Program.
One of the key tools we have to support your selling efforts is a SunPower Dealer Portal that provides access to online ordering, design tools, our Marketing Resource Center, SunPower University, Dealer Program Guidelines, data sheets, logos and more.
As part of our 'On Boarding' process, we need to provide user access to the portal for the appropriate personnel at your company. We have attached an Excel file that you can use to provide us with contact information. Please complete this and return it to SunPower NA Partner Account Management via email. Once we receive this completed contact sheet from you, we will load your employees into the dealer portal and send each user an email giving them access.
Please also submit an updated copy of your Contractor's license to maintain your access to online ordering. It is important to keep your license updated to ensure that you can request cash orders as needed, and that all of your orders are processed on time. Kindly send the Contractor's license to RACompliance@sunpowercorp.com.
In addition, while your local sales manager is your primary contact with SunPower, please be aware that the email addresses below serve as excellent resources if you have questions that can potentially be easily answered via email. The support teams behind these email addresses have deep knowledge and respond quickly.
Partner Portal Management: partnerportal@sunpowercorp.com
Marketing (Tools and Campaigns): marketing@sunpowercorp.com Consumer Financing: financing@sunpowercorp.com Training: training_support@sunpowercorp.com Past, Present & Future orders: ____psr@sunpowercorp.com Technical Support: technical.support@sunpowercorp.com Credit for you, our dealer partners: credit@sunpowercorp.com
We look forward to growing with you.
Sincerely,
Your SunPower Team
77 Rio Robles San Jose, CA 95134 Phone: 408.240.5580 Fax: 408.240.5400 www.sunpowercorp.com
